        <h2 property="dc:title"><a href="/blog/175725/populist-insurgency-new-york-city" title="A Populist Insurgency in New York City">A Populist Insurgency in New York City</a></h2>
     
  <div class="byline"><a href="/authors/katrina-vanden-heuvel">Katrina vanden Heuvel</a> <span class="timestamp"><abbr class="published" title="2013-08-13T10:04:40-14400">on August 13, 2013 - 10:04 AM ET</abbr></span></div>  
  <div class="content">
